title: The King of Swag? Check out these Photos of Celeb Stylist Toyin Lawani’s Son as he turns 3
text:
The King of Swag? Check out these Photos of Celeb Stylist Toyin Lawani’s Son as he turns 3 03.01.2017 at By BellaNaija.com 2 Comments 
Lord Maine , son of celeb stylist and designer Toyin Lawani , turned 3 years old on the first of January and his mum has shared several new photos from a recent shoot to celebrate. 
In some photos you can see her son posing next to two armed police escorts, in other photos he’s rocking a fur coat in style.
